INSTALLATION:
1)Extract the folders "PSP", "cxmb", "PICTURE", and
"seplugins" from "[PSP] Custom Theme Pack - CXMB - 
5.00 M33-6.rar"
2)Connect your PSP to your computer via USB
3)Open your PSP on your computer
4)Copy the folder named "PSP" into your PSP's memory 
stick
5)Copy the folder named "cxmb" into your PSP's memory 
stick
6)If you already have a folder named "seplugins" and 
a text file called "vsh.txt" in it then paste the 
following line in it and save it: ms0:/cxmb/cxmb.prx 1
7)If you do not have a folder called "seplugins" then 
copy the extracted "seplugins" folder to your PSP's
memory stick
8)Copy the "PICTURE" folder to your PSP's memory stick
9)Disconnect and reboot your PSP
10)Go to "settings" and "themes" on your PSP's XMB
11)Select the theme you want to use
